OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1775740267
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 23 Apr to Thu 7 May
OL,6,FBlocked patterns with high pressure
OL,7,Fnear to the UK will probably be
OL,8,Fdominant during this period with a
OL,9,Fgood deal of dry weather across the UK
OL,10,Fas whole. Some unsettled interludes
OL,11,Fcould develop at times, especially in
OL,12,Fthe south, where rainfall amounts
OL,13,Fcould be above average at times.
OL,14,FTemperatures will probably be near to
OL,15,For slightly above normal, although
OL,16,Fsome cold nights are still possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
